Transition Music: watson - 潮騒アーベント https://youtu.be/y6Z0p6C7Prk
Editor's Commentary: So, I originally didn't intend for this to be a collaborative video. I wanted to make a huge edit of every House Flipper stream Jerma's done, and I started working on editing the first House Flipper stream around October or November of 2021. However, I kept losing interest or wanting to work on other projects, so I didn't have it finished until December 8, 2021. I finished editing about half of the second stream before I got distracted by other projects again, until February 24, 2022, when I talked to some other independent Jerma editors and suggested collaborating on editing all of Jerma's House Flipper streams, because at the rate I was working, I was never going to finish. They liked the idea, so we chose which streams we were interested in editing. I had already finished working on stream #1 and was halfway through stream #2, and I decided to also edit stream #5. I promise you'll see a lot less of me in the second part.
